entries.femaleVariant: Dis way.
You know Pacifica well?
Nah. You guys aren't exactly great at rollin' out the welcome mat for outsiders.
Grann Ertha.
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Placide, pitit mwen." t="Placide, my child." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Pou ou." t="For you." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Ou pa t 'bezwen…" t="You didn't have to…" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Petèt, men sa se pou ou. P’ap pran “non” pou yon repons." t="Maybe. But this is yours. Won't take \"no\" for an answer." b="" a=""/>
<mothertongue l="creo" m="Vini nan." b="" a=" We talk here."/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Gen lòt ki genyen li pi mal…" t="Others have it worse…" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Mèsi." t="Thank you." b="" a=""/>
Let's go. Not far now.
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Aye, Placide." t="Hey, Placide." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Mwen pral deplase yo ankò." t="Gonna move 'em all over again." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Ki etaj?" t="Which floor?" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Dezyèm." t="Second." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Placide! Mwen gen sa ou te bay lòd." t="Placide! Got your order ready." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Li pa konekte ak Agwè depi Josue ... ou konnen kisa pou w fè." t="She hasn't jacked into Agwe since Josue... So you know what to do." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Li si sansib ke sa?" t="She's that sensitive?" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Li pa ta pran yon souf san li pa di-sa." t="She wouldn't take a breath without his say-so." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Oke mwen pral vini pita." t="OK! I'll come later." b="" a=""/>
You deal wid Animal before?
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Sibil pa ap renmen sa." t="Sibil won't like that." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Ki diferans ki genyen?" t="What's the difference?" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Li pa leve pou yon anè, nenpòt jan." t="She hasn't got up for a year now, anyway." b="" a=""/>
Yeah. A few times.
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Lovelie? Oh tanpri. Josue te toujou genyen li nan yon kòd." t="Lovelie? Oh please. Josue always had her on a leash." b="" a=""/>
Pacifica's biggest, ugliest temple to greed... but never finished.
Until last week it was deserted, empty.
But now?
De Animals crawled in, made a nest.
I mean, it makes no sense, them being here.
You want the Animals out of the GIM? Extinct?
They tryna provoke you? Make you do somethin' stupid?
That why you hired me?
You learn everyt'ing soon.
Middle of Pacifica, no backup, cut off…
It's your turf. Hell, even badges don't patrol around here.
Dey do not leave GIM.
How many we talkin' about in there?
Thirty. Maybe more.
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Oke, jijman ta dwe pase pa kounye a." t="Well, judgment should be passed by now." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Menm si li mache alè, li p'ap janm mete konfyans lan neg lan." t="Even if he walks away from this, she'll never trust him again." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Hm. E li te tèlman enpòtan." t="Hm. And he was so important." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Placide! Ou gen yon minit?" t="Placide! Do you have a minute?" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Pa jodi a." t="Not today." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Men, ou te di…" t="But you said…" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Pita, Emilie, mwen pap bliye." t="Later, Emilie – I haven't forgotten." b="" a=""/>
Our interest is now in de GIM – de Grand Imperial Mall.
Was to be its own city, where suits would burn their eddies.
A closed circle. De corps feed their sheep, they spit de cash back out. All de toys here are grown from corpo cash.
V?
I must wait long?
You are coming?
Welcome to Pacifica.
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Tonnè, fout nou deyò, banfout sèpan! Tounen nan vil la! Se Pasifika!" t="Get the fuck out, snakes! Back to the city! This is Pacifica!" b="" a=""/>
Has Holt's campaign promise, and I quote…
Pacifica – a hotbed of controversy, a city within the city.
All that and more...
"I will clean up Pacifica, set it straight."
Already proved to be false?
We decided to take a closer look.
A dirty stain on Night City's map…
Or a chance at urban renewal?
Uh-huh.
